ing Management Institute needed a coach.\u00a0 I paid a lot of money, but it was worth 10 times what I paid.\u00a0 Anyway, enough about me, let's talk about you.<\/p><p>A coach can help you in all aspects of your career and life, and after coaching hundreds of engineers, I know I can help you.\u00a0 Due to time constraints, I can only coach a small number of engineers at one time, but if you complete the form below, you will be considered.\u00a0 Please answer all of the questions below and expect to hear from us within one business day.<\/p><p>Please note, this is a paid for service, if you don't have the money, consider <a href=\"http:\/\/engineeringmanagementinstitute.org\/ask-a-question\/\">asking a question<\/a> that we can answer through our content channels.<\/p><p>- Anthony Fasano, PE, Engineering Management Institute<\/p>","pa_condition_repeater":[],"premium_tooltip_text":"Hi, I'm a global tooltip.","premium_tooltip_position":"top,bottom"},"elements":[],"isInner":false,"widgetType":"text-editor","elType":"widget"},{"id":"5019d8ca","settings":{"shortcode":"[gravityform id=\"56\" title=\"false\" description=\"false\"]","pa_condition_repeater":[],"premium_tooltip_text":"Hi, I'm a global tooltip.","premium_tooltip_position":"top,bottom"},"elements":[],"isInner":false,"widgetType":"shortcode","elType":"widget"}],"isInner":false,"elType":"column"}],"isInner":false,"elType":"section"}],"settings":{"template":"default","hide_title":"yes"},"metadata":{"be_title_toggle_hide":"1","socialize_text":"If you enjoyed this post, please consider <a href=\"#comments\">leaving a comment<\/a> or <a href=\"http:\/\/engineeringmanagementinstitute.org\/feed\/\" title=\"Syndicate this site using RSS\">subscribing to the <abbr title=\"Really Simple Syndication\">RSS<\/abbr> feed<\/a> to have future articles delivered to your feed reader.","socialize":"2,1,22,24","_yoast_wpseo_content_score":"90","swp_open_graph_image_data":"false","swp_open_graph_image_url":"","swp_cache_timestamp":"